1. *Želeli* smo da bude lepo vreme za naš odmor. (We wanted it to be nice weather for our vacation.) 
2. *Želeo* je da učestvuje u svim takmičenjima. (He wanted to participate in all competitions.)
3. *Želele* su da proslave svoje prvo rođendane skupa. (They wanted to celebrate their first birthdays together.)
4. *Želeli* smo da se svi sastanemo na jednom mestu. (We wanted to meet all of us in one place.)
5. *Želelo* se da se sve bude isplanirano unapred. (It was wanted that everything would be planned in advance.)